name: Cubyte (itch)
description:
Cubyte is a game where you are a circle that journeys through danger. Prepare to face different types of enemies that each want to bring you down! Your objective is to get to a portal which will bring you to the next level. Green squares (Icues) will help and guide you through your journey.

INFO: This is the first game that I have ever created. I am not a professional. Thank you for even looking at the page of my game; I really appreciate it.
